{"tid":54080,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"睇唔透「拍拖」既關係","createTime":"2016-12-25T08:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T09:58:17.000Z","uid":57548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24ab5556bb387f66a390a81e92dd5a0c8d531b1a","tid":54080,"uid":57548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"身邊有好多人拍拖，但係佢地仲撩其他異性。<br />\n我講個種「撩」係大家日日曖昧呀 kiss呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但明明有男/女朋友！ <br />\n係唔係我諗得「拍拖」咁簡單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上到大學，好多情侶都係各有各玩。<br />\n每一次聽朋友講佢地點樣撩其他女仔，我都覺得好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我只係純粹發洩下 因為好唔明白 <br />\n大家都可以分享下身邊朋友拍拖，但又「撩」異性既事蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615d184b1d2a388c721f1549de47dc67888b6f7f","tid":54080,"uid":27985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"屌好仆街"},{"pid":"829b6eded99a0b8a53d2583b530cd8700a8543a1","tid":54080,"uid":58810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:58:17.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}